::Scavenger::

Scavenger looks down at what he has in his hand, but before he can explain, he hears Hook and Scrapper. He looks between the two of them.

"Right. That's what I was looking for."

Turning around, he walks back out of the room, searching for the hyperdrive.

> ::Scrapper/Dreadwing/Needlenose/Havotron::
> Scrapper smiled. "He will never find waht we need, he is useless as 
> always."
> 
> Dreadwing did not find it funny.  "We must finish soon, the Autobots 
> prepare to leave and you sit around making jokes. Havotron will be 
> displeased."
> 
> Needlenose looked to Spinister then to Havotron. Not knowing what to 
> do he to bowed but did not say a thing.
